Issue.creator: sambhavdutt
Issue.summary: Add `latest` tagged thirdparty images to daily Behave tests.
Issue.description: There are no `latest` tagged thirdparty images and the Behave tests are looking for the `latest` image which doesn't exist as the thirdparty images in the CI have a different tag. This change is to pull the thirdparty images and tag to `latest` to allow the normal testing in the Behave tests.
